        <h2>Storyline</h2>
        
        <div class="inline canwrap" itemprop="description">
            <p>
Epic tale of a group of Jewish gangsters in New York, from childhood, through their glory years during prohibition, and their meeting again 35 years later.                <em class="nobr">Written by
<a href="/search/title?plot_author=Andrew%20Welsh%20%3Candreww%40bnr.ca%3E&view=simple&sort=alpha&ref_=tt_stry_pl"
>Andrew Welsh &lt;andreww@bnr.ca&gt;</a></em>            </p>
        </div>
        
        <span class="see-more inline"> 
                <a href="/title/tt0087843/plotsummary?ref_=tt_stry_pl"
>Plot Summary</a>
    <span>|</span>
        <a href="/title/tt0087843/synopsis?ref_=tt_stry_pl"
>Plot Synopsis</a>
    </span>
        <hr />
